snippet.title: Jana On Camera
snippet.description: Hello! My name is Jana Nascimento Nagase and I'm a journalist and film critic who attends press junkets, press screening, roundtables of the biggest movies here in the US.  Here on YouTube I'll feature interviews with footage, clips, and behind the scenes from the latest movies.
